ologisk Museum, Copenhagen, Denmark. Photo by Department of Paleobiology, National Museum of Natural History, Washington DC, USA." httpUri-0="https://zenodo.org/record/583184/files/figure.png" httpUri-1="https://zenodo.org/record/583185/files/figure.png" httpUri-2="https://zenodo.org/record/583186/files/figure.png" httpUri-3="https://zenodo.org/record/583187/files/figure.png" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">Figs. 1–5</figureCitation>
