<bibRefCitation author="Murata" box="[151,457,582,607]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" refString="Murata, Y. (1998) Notes on the evolutionary process of butterflies and butterfly fossils. Butterflies, 20 (part 1 &amp; 2), 4 - 17 &amp; 27 - 40. [in Japanese with English summary]" type="journal article" year="1998">Murata (1998: Figs 53–55)</bibRefCitation>
